      "content": "idk i really dont want to go to the er if i dont have to it's so expensive and the wait is always crazy. i get these bad migraines sometimes and usually the face feeling happens when they are really intense. if i just take the sumatriptan and some ibuprofen it'll probably settle down in an hour right? it doesn't feel like a stroke, it just feels like a really heavy pressure.",
